"label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recmCkLvUxpY51bJB","ref":"1Kgs.1.1","text":"Now king David was old and stricken in years; and they covered him with clothes, but he gat no heat.","year":-1015},{"id":"reckdZkNk43koX9gT","ref":"1Kgs.1.2","text":"Wherefore his servants said unto him, Let there be sought for my lord the king a young virgin: and let her stand before the king, and let her cherish him, and let her lie in thy bosom, that my lord the king may get heat.","year":-1015},{"id":"recBCthvGStSRfwTt","ref":"1Kgs.1.3","text":"So they sought for a fair damsel throughout all the coasts of Israel, and found Abishag a Shunammite, and brought her to the king.","year":-1015},{"id":"recHtUeoXvTQ9Lm4h","ref":"1Kgs.1.4","text":"And the damsel was very fair, and cherished the king, and ministered to him: but the king knew her not.","year":-1015},{"id":"recnvHLRJI9WRET1f","ref":"1Kgs.1.5","text":"Then Adonijah the son of Haggith exalted himself, saying, I will be king: and he prepared him chariots and horsemen, and fifty men to run before him.","year":-1015},{"id":"rec9lN7bK2L1Hle1n","ref":"1Kgs.1.6","text":"And his father had not displeased him at any time in saying, Why hast thou done so? and he also was a very goodly man; and his mother bare him after Absalom.","year":-1015}]}
